						<p>On the east wall of the central shrine in the Naṭanapādēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Vikramachōḷa. Year 11: 1128-29 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This inscription records a gift of a <hi rend="italic">sandhi</hi> lamp to God Tirukkaṇṇīśvaram-uḍaiya Mahādēva of Śōḻakulavallinallūr•••• in Rājarāja-vaḷanāḍu.</p>						

